name: Green Topography 001
description:
Aerial maps of imaginary worlds.

Springing from an unintended feature in my code, these pieces explore the latent space within a generative adversarial network that was supposed to be learning to upscale images in interesting ways.

Enjoy exploring a predominantly green series of verdant landscapes, mountains, ridges, and valleys.
